Package arcade.patch.agent.module

Class PatchModuleCytotoxicity

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.patch.agent.module.PatchModule
      • arcade.patch.agent.module.PatchModuleCytotoxicity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module
    public class PatchModuleCytotoxicity
extends PatchModule
    Implementation of Module for killing tissue agents.

    PatchModuleCytotoxicity is stepped once after a CD8 CAR T-cell binds to a target tissue cell. The PatchModuleCytotoxicity determines if cell has enough granzyme to kill. If so, it kills cell and calls the reset to neutral helper to return to neutral state. If not, it waits until it has enough granzyme to kill cell.
